Company Overview of Companhia de Locação das Américas



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Companhia de Locação das Américas provides vehicle rental services with or without drivers for small, medium, and large companies in Brazil. It also sells its used vehicles in the wholesale and retail markets. As of March 31, 2017, the company’s fleet consisted of 27,628 cars. Companhia de Locação das Américas was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Belo Horizonte, Brazil.


Avenida Raja Gabaglia, nº 1.78112º andarLuxemburgoBelo Horizonte, MG 30350-540BrazilFounded in 1993616 Employees



