Companhia de Locação das Américas Key Developments

Companhia de Locação das Américas, Q1 2017 Earnings Call, May 04, 2017
May 4 17
Companhia de Locação das Américas, Q1 2017 Earnings Call, May 04, 2017


Companhia de Locação das Américas S.A. Announces Consolidated Earnings Results for the Fourth Quarter and Year Ended December 31, 2016
Mar 13 17
Companhia de Locação das Américas S.A. announced consolidated earnings results for the fourth quarter and year ended December 31, 2016. For the quarter, the company reported operational revenues of BRL 188,861,000 compared with BRL 178,866,000 for the same period a year ago. Operating income EBIT was BRL 38,356,000 compared with BRL 32,732,000 for the same period a year ago. Earnings before tax was BRL 11,579,000 compared with BRL 3,567,000 for the same period a year ago. Net Income was BRL 7,797,000 compared with BRL 2,353,000 for the same period a year ago. EBITDA was BRL 62,435,000 compared with BRL 58,478,000 for the same period a year ago. 

For the year, the company reported operational revenues of BRL 754,714,000 compared with BRL 708,216,000 for the same period a year ago. Operating income EBIT BRL 150,325,000 compared with BRL 124,310,000 for the same period a year ago. Earnings before tax was BRL 22,452,000 compared with BRL 31,006,000 for the same period a year ago. Earnings after tax was BRL 35,821,000 compared with BRL 22,452,000 for the same period a year ago. Net Income was BRL 28,907,000 compared with BRL 18,561,000 for the same period a year ago. EBITDA was BRL 248,826,000 compared with BRL 222,758,000 for the same period a year ago. Net cash provided by operating activities was BRL 251,049,000 compared with BRL 175,993,000 for the same period a year ago. Acquisition of other fixed assets and intangible was BRL 4,439,000 compared with BRL 3,682,000 for the same period a year ago. Net debt at the end of the year, was BRL 627.9 million.


Companhia de Locação das Américas Announces Consolidated Earnings and Operating Results for the Third Quarter and Nine Months of 2016
Oct 26 16
Companhia de Locação das Américas announced consolidated earnings and operating results for the third quarter and nine months of 2016. For the quarter, total net revenue was BRL 201.707 million compared to BRL 178.415 million a year ago. Net rental revenue was BRL 102.0 million compared to BRL 97.0 million a year ago. EBITDA was BRL 63.0 million compared to BRL 56.2 million a year ago. EBIT was BRL 38.5 million compared to BRL 31.8 million a year ago. Net income was BRL 8.0 million compared to BRL 4.4 million a year ago. Net debt was BRL 624.5 million against BRL 693.7 million a year ago.

For the nine months, total net revenue was BRL 565.9 million compared to BRL 529.4 million a year ago. Net rental revenue was BRL 304.4 million compared to BRL 291.5 million a year ago. EBITDA was BRL 186.4 million compared to BRL 164.3 million a year ago. EBIT was BRL 112.0 million compared to BRL 91.6 million a year ago. Net income was BRL 21.1 million compared to BRL 16.2 million a year ago. Net cash provided by operating activities was BRL 192.912 million. Acquisition of other fixed assets and intangible was BRL 2.229 million. 

For the quarter, the company reported average operating fleet of 24,086 against 23,089 a year ago. Fleet in deployment was 1,904 against 3,427 a year ago.


