Companhia de Locacao das Americas to establish new branch
Tuesday, 14 Jun 2016 08:47am EDT 
Companhia de Locacao das Americas :Announced on Monday that the board of directors approved to establish a new branch of the company, to be located in Belo Horizonte (Minas Gerais). 
			
