Companhia de Locacao das Americas announces own capital interest payment
Monday, 28 Mar 2016 04:47pm EDT 
Companhia de Locacao das Americas:Says that its board of directors has approved own capital interest payment totaling gross 3.9 million Brazilian reais, or 0.061 reais per share.Payment date is April 29.Record date March 28.Shares will be traded as ex-interest as of March 29. 
			
