Companhia de Locacao das Americas announces own capital interest payment date
Tuesday, 22 Mar 2016 07:30am EDT 
Companhia de Locacao das Americas:Says its Board has agreed that payment of own capital interest announced on March 23, June 24 and Sept. 21, 2015 will be made on April 1. 
			
