Patria Investimentos Ltda reaches 21.63 pct of Companhia de Locacao das Americas' ordinary shares
Thursday, 22 Oct 2015 07:53am EDT 
Companhia de Locacao das Americas:Says that funds managed by Patria Investimentos Ltda are holding a total of 14,078,520 ordinary shares of the company, representing around 21.63 pct of all the shares issued by the company. 
			
