					Full Description



		Companhia de Locacao das Americas is a Brazil-based company mainly involved in the leasing of motor vehicles. The Company is primarily active in the leasing of domestic and imported vehicles, with or without drivers. The Company’s portfolio includes motorcycles, passenger cars and trucks, among others. Through its subsidiaries, the Company operates in a number of Brazilian states. The Company's principal operating units are located in cities of Sao Paulo, Belo Horizonte, Rio de Janeiro, Curitiba, Vitoria, Salvador, Fortaleza, Porto Alegre, Curitiba, Cuiaba, Brasilia, Belem and Manaus. As of December 31, 2011, the Company's fleet consisted of 27,262 cars. As of December 31, 2011, the Company had two subsidiaries: Agile Car Ltda and Locarvel Locadora de Veiculos Ltda.
» Full Overview of LCAM3.SA







