Company Description                    




                        Headquartered in 1993 in Sao Paulo - SP it is a full service vehicle rental company, providing customization, planning, management, and leasing service to more than 200 institutional clients in Brazil ranking among the top 3 companies in the sector. Among the vehicles leased by the company are: cars, trucks, SUVs, armored vehicles and motorcycles. With a team of 650 employees, the company posted BRL 390.7mn (USD 233.9mn) in revenues in 2011, an increase of 26.4% year-on-year basis.                    


